				def count(f):
					n = 0
					def wrapper(*args, **kwargs):
						nonlocal n
						n += 1
						print('Called {} times'.format(n))
						return f(*args, **kwargs)
					return wrapper
				
				@count
				def hello():
					print("hello world !")
